implements java.util.SortedSet<E>, ArrayBackedSet<E>, java.io.Serializable
    A SortedSet backed by an array of elements. The array is the exact length required to contain the elements. Elements are tested using a binary search implementation. The set may also be view as a List, which implements the RandomAccess interface to indicate constant time random access.
